Package fr.maxlego08.itemstacker.zcore.utils.storage

Interface Savable

All Known Implementing Classes:
CooldownBuilder, MessageLoader
public interface Savable
The Savable interface represents objects that can be saved and loaded using a provided Persist object. Implement this interface in classes that need to be serialized and deserialized.
